## Limitations

The findings in this report are based on available online resources and may not capture the full complexity of migrant integration challenges across different regions and contexts. The data is primarily focused on high-income countries, and there is a lack of comprehensive data from low-income regions. Additionally, the perspectives gathered from community-based platforms may not fully represent expert opinions or the latest research developments in the field.